Title: Teso Dos Bichos
Plot: The unearthing of an ancient Ecuadorian Amaru urn and its removal to America despite protests leads to a series of deaths linked to a shaman spirit released by the urn.
GuestStars: Vic Trevino, Janne Mortil, Tom McBeath, Gordon Tootoosis, Ron Suave, Alan Robertson, Garrison Chrisjohn
